tweetSentenceList.constTree: (ROOT (S (NP (DT Another) (NN day)) (VP (VBN spent) (PP (IN in) (NP (PRP$ my) (NN bed)))) (. .)))
tweetSentenceList.depTree: [spent/VBN nsubj>[day/NN det>Another/DT] nmod:in>[bed/NN case>in/IN nmod:poss>my/PRP$] punct>./.]

tweetSentenceList.constTree: (ROOT (S (NP (PRP I)) (ADVP (RB really)) (VP (MD should) (VP (VB get) (NP (DT a) (NN life)))) (. .)))
tweetSentenceList.depTree: [get/VB nsubj>I/PRP advmod>really/RB aux>should/MD dobj>[life/NN det>a/DT] punct>./.]
